|                  |          | hot code push | page reload |            |        |
+------------------+----------+---------------+-------------+------------+--------+
| local storage	   | No       | Yes           | Yes         | EJSON-able | Local  |
+------------------+----------+---------------+-------------+------------+--------+
| Session variable | Yes      | Yes           | No          | EJSON-able | Global |
+------------------+----------+---------------+-------------+------------+--------+
| ReactiveVar      | Yes      | No            | ?           | any        | Local  |
+------------------+----------+---------------+-------------+------------+--------+
| ReactiveDict     | Yes      | If named      | ?           | any        | Local  |
+------------------+----------+---------------+-------------+------------+--------+
